      <pattern name="aichatcontextmap routing" location="docs/architecture/SPAARKEAI-WORKSPACE-ARCHITECTURE.md">SpaarkeAi looks up the right playbook by entity logical name; the no-context default is the null/empty key row.</pattern>
    </patterns>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check: confirm working tree clean, dependencies (tasks 013 schema, 025 always-on tools, 032 InteractiveInChatGateResolver) marked ✅ in `TASK-INDEX.md`. (task-execute Step 0)</step>
    <step order="1">Read all files in `&lt;knowledge&gt;&lt;files&gt;` — especially design.md §7.4.3 (the verbatim system prompt) and the `jps-playbook-design` skill workflow.</step>
    <step order="2">Locate the existing `Deploy-Playbook.ps1` (or equivalent seed script) via `Glob scripts/Deploy-Playbook*.ps1`. Confirm its parameter contract (environment URL, solution prefix, JSON file path). If absent, the task's deployment step (step 5) uses the `dataverse-deploy` skill's record-upsert pattern instead.</step>
    <step order="3">Author `infra/insights/schemas/playbook-spaarke-assistant-general.json` with the following fields populated:
      - `sprk_name`: `"spaarke-assistant-general"`
      - `sprk_displayname`: `"Spaarke Assistant — General"`
      - `sprk_systemprompt`: the verbatim text from design.md §7.4.3 (multi-paragraph; preserve markdown emphasis and bullet styling)
      - `sprk_alwaysontools`: JSON array containing exactly the 6 tool ids (3 meta-tools + 3 foundational tools)
      - `sprk_defaultgateresolver`: `"InteractiveInChatGateResolver"`
      - `sprk_modeltier`: `"Standard"`
      - `sprk_costbudget`: `"Cheap"`
      - `sprk_latencybudget`: `"Sub10s"`
      - `sprk_featureflagref`: `"feature.actionEngine.assistantDefault"` (ADR-018)
      - `sprk_iskillswitched`: `false` (default — flag is opt-out)
    </step>
    <step order="4">Add a `sprk_aichatcontextmap` row for the no-context default landing: `sprk_entitylogicalname`: null/empty, `sprk_playbookref`: the playbook from step 3 (by `sprk_name`), `sprk_displaylabel`: `"No-context default (SpaarkeAi landing)"`. This row lives in the same JSON file under an `aichatcontextmap` key, or in a sibling file — follow `jps-playbook-design` skill convention.</step>
    <step order="5">Deploy: run `scripts/Deploy-Playbook.ps1 -EnvironmentUrl https://{org}.crm.dynamics.com -JsonPath infra/insights/schemas/playbook-spaarke-assistant-general.json` (or the equivalent invocation per skill convention). Capture stdout/stderr to `notes/deploys/052-default-playbook-seed.md`.</step>
    <step order="6">Verify in Dataverse: query `sprk_playbook` filtered by `sprk_name eq 'spaarke-assistant-general'` — exactly one record exists with the expected fields. Use the `dataverse:dv-python-sdk` skill or `pac data query` for the check.</step>
    <step order="7">**Idempotency verification**: re-run the deploy script. Confirm record count = 1 (no duplicate). Capture proof in `notes/deploys/052-default-playbook-seed.md`.</step>
    <step order="8">Update `current-task.md` with progress; checkpoint via `context-handoff` skill.</step>
    <step order="9">Update `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`: mark task 052 status ✅. Update `current-task.md`: task 052 complete; unblocks tasks 053, 054, 055 (parallel group E).</step>
    <step order="10">If any deviations from this plan, document in `projects/ai-spaarke-action-engine-r1/notes/handoffs/052-deviations.md`.</step>
  </steps>

